    "Relational context extracted from the dialogue could then be applied as relational frames connecting the concepts and be represented as hyperedges within the hypergraph.",
    "Then the cluster analysis plus high relational density mapping could be conducted to objectively identify perspectivetaking (ToM) in action.",
    "This could be made even more precise with additional sentiment analysis that could then be used to gauge the emotional tone, and entity recognition to understand the subjects discussed.",
    "To explore syntactic relations, dependency parsing could be employed that signify understanding or lack thereof.",
    "Interaction weights analysis could also be used to explore the neural network weights that activate in response to different types of input."
